<HEADLINE>
<P>
METROPOLITAN DIGEST / LOS ANGELES COUNTY NEWS IN BRIEF: PASADENA; CALTECH SIGNS 
NEW CONTRACT TO MANAGE JPL FOR NASA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Caltech has signed a five-year contract to continue managing the Jet 
Propulsion Laboratory for NASA, it was announced this week. 
</P>
<P>
 Considered the National Aeronautics and Space Administration's leading center 
for space exploration, JPL managed the Galileo space mission to Jupiter and the 
Magellan mission to Venus. Caltech has managed JPL since NASA's inception in 
1958. 
</P>
</TEXT>
