<TEXT>
<P>
 An Oxnard man pleaded innocent Friday to the Christmas Day stabbing of his 
ex-girlfriend's son. 
</P>
<P>
 Ventura County Municipal Judge Bruce A. Clark continued bail at $250,000 for 
32-year-old Jose Socorro Jimenez. 
</P>
<P>
 Clark also set a preliminary hearing for Feb. 9 to determine whether Jimenez 
will stand trial on the matter. 
</P>
<P>
 Witnesses said Jimenez stabbed 21-year-old Isaias Guerrero after showing up at 
the family's Campbell Way home about 3 a.m. 
</P>
