 Before the stabbing, the victim had tried to get Jimenez off the family's 
property, witnesses said. Jimenez had smashed his hand against a living-room 
window, yelling that the victim's mother, 36-year-old Graciela Guerrero, was 
"going to pay" for breaking off their three-year relationship. 
