<HEADLINE>
<P>
TUCHMAN SET TO JURY 'NEW DIRECTIONS' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Maurice Tuchman, senior curator of 20th-Century Art at the Los Angeles County 
Museum of Art, will jury "New Directions in the '90s," a national juried 
exhibition being held in March at the Hello Artichoke gallery in Los Feliz. 
</P>
<P>
 The entry deadline is Feb. 10. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: (213) 953-4835. 
</P>
</TEXT>
