<DOCNO> LA011594-0254 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 004357 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 15, 1994, Saturday, Southland Edition 
</P>
