<HEADLINE>
<P>
GIRLS' BASKETBALL ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In other Garden Grove League games: 
</P>
<P>
 Garden Grove 43, Santiago 32 -- Garden Grove (4-10, 2-4) fell behind, 16-8, 
