down from 120 to 85; men's basketball from 20 or more to 13. Where did these 
scholarships go? To women athletes -- basketball, soccer, track, volleyball, 
etc. -- this was well deserved and long overdue. 
</P>
<P>
 Do these black men's basketball coaches want these scholarships back from the 
women? Are these women athletes somehow less deserving than the men? 
</P>
<P>
