O'Neill added 13 to lead the visiting Falcons (11-6, 1-2) in the Pacific League 
game. Hoover missed 13 of 18 free throws down the stretch, four at the front 
end of one-and-one opportunities. 
</P>
<P>
 Chaminade 52, Crespi 44 -- Mike Yang scored 13 points and Casey Cote grabbed 
13 rebounds to lead the host Eagles (5-10, 1-5) to their first Mission League 
victory, snapping Crespi's four-game winning streak. Junior forward Gianandrea 
