<P>
 Cleveland 54, Reseda 19 -- Teresa McGuire scored 14 points and grabbed nine 
rebounds to lead the Cavaliers (3-7, 1-2) in a Northwest Valley Conference 
game. 
</P>
<P>
 Monroe 47, Grant 35 -- Senior center Dimara Haymond scored 19 points and 
grabbed 18 rebounds to lead the visiting Vikings (9-7, 2-2) in the Valley Pac-8 
Conference game. 
</P>
<P>
 Faith Baptist 60, Campbell Hall 56 -- Shawn Dennis had 21 points for the 
Contenders and Amanda Warren scored a career-high 17 in a losing effort for the 
Vikings. 
</P>
